extends ../layout/layout.pug

block variables
    - var current_page = 'portfolio'

block content
    .mx-auto.container.wh-container
        h1.text-4xl.font-serif.mb-10(class="desktop:text-6xl desktop:mb-14")
            | Stability from real estate. 
            br
            | Yield from expertise.

        .buildings-banner                                              
        div(class="desktop:grid desktop:grid-cols-3")
            .mb-10(class="desktop:mb-15")
                div(class="desktop:text-xl desktop:pr-30")
                    | Our holdings consist of real estate backed claims and real estate owned assets including performing assets.
            div
                .mb-10(class="desktop:mb-15")
                    .font-serif.text-8xl.mb-2
                        span.text-grey-4
                            | €
                        span 131.5M
                    .font-medium
                        | market value of real estate collateral
                .mb-10(class="desktop:mb-15")
                    .font-serif.text-8xl.mb-2
                        span 28.6%
                    .font-medium
                        | Net Debt to MV   
            div
                .mb-10(class="desktop:mb-15")
                    .font-serif.text-8xl.mb-2
                        span >500
                    .font-medium
                        | portfolios analysed 
                .mb-10(class="desktop:mb-15")
                    .font-serif.text-8xl.mb-2
                        span 28
                    .font-medium
                        | portfolios acquired  in 5 jurisdictions since 2019
        .mb-6    
            .text-bronze-1.flex.items-center
                +svg-icon(svg-icon-name='vector')
                span.text-2xl.ml-1.font-medium
                    | Real Estate Values by Country
                
        h2.text-4xl.font-serif.mb-6(class="desktop:text-5xl desktop:mb-10")
            | We specialize in managing a diversified portfolio in Europe   
        div(class="desktop:grid desktop:grid-cols-2")    
            .mb-10(class="desktop:text-xl desktop:pr-30")
                | that are geographically stratified, encompassing key markets. This strategic distribution mitigates risk and enables us to leverage our regional expertise to unlock the potential of each asset.
            .mb-10
                div(class="desktop:flex")
                    .mb-10(class="desktop:pr-15")
                        img(src=require("../assets/pie1.svg"))
                    .mb-10 
                        ol(class="desktop:text-xl")
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 1.
                                span Croatia 9.74M
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 2.
                                span Slovenia 11.18M
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 3.
                                span Serbia 10.27M
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 4.
                                span Greece 2.30M
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 5.
                                span Montenegro 0.26M
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 6.
                                span Spain 97.76M        
        .portfolio-map   

        .mb-6    
            .text-bronze-1.flex.items-center
                +svg-icon(svg-icon-name='vector')
                span.text-2xl.ml-1.font-medium
                    | Real Estate Values by Type
   
        h2.text-4xl.font-serif.mb-6(class="desktop:text-5xl desktop:mb-10")
            | Our holdings include a mix of real estate
        div(class="desktop:grid desktop:grid-cols-2")    
            .mb-10(class="desktop:text-xl desktop:pr-30")
                | Our holdings include a mix of real estate back claims and real estate owned assets encompassing land, residential and commercial properties.
            .mb-10
                div(class="desktop:flex")
                    .mb-10(class="desktop:pr-15")
                        img(src=require("../assets/pie2.svg"))
                    .mb-10 
                        ol(class="desktop:text-xl")
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 1.
                                span Land 18.68M
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 2.
                                span Commercial 41.93M
                            li.mb-3
                                span.mr-4.font-medium 3.
                                span Residential 70.91M
                                                                                                                                                
        .mb-6    
            .text-bronze-1.flex.items-center
                +svg-icon(svg-icon-name='vector')
                span.text-2xl.ml-1.font-medium
                    | Portfolio Management
        h2.text-4xl.font-serif.mb-6(class="desktop:text-5xl desktop:mb-10")
            | Meet our platform LISA
        div(class="desktop:grid desktop:grid-cols-2 desktop:mb-6")    
            .mb-10(class="desktop:text-xl desktop:pr-30")
                | Lynxcap Investment Software Application or LISA for short is our proprietary platform that allows us to achieve operational and cost efficiency.
            .mb-10
                img.size-full(src=require("../assets/laptop.png"))

        .mb-10(class="desktop:grid desktop:grid-cols-3 desktop:gap-10 large:gap-14")                        
            .mb-10
                .text-2xl.font-serif.mb-3(class="desktop:text-4xl")
                    | Accessed from anywhere at anytime  
                div(class="desktop:text-xl")
                    | In addition to a number of tools developed and hosted internally, LynxCap utilizes third party cloud solutions for reporting and ticketing. Using secured connections, these can be accessed from anywhere at anytime which also allows us to focus on our own strengths for internal applications. 
            .mb-10
                .text-2xl.font-serif.mb-3(class="desktop:text-4xl")
                    | Link between certified partners and legal offices  
                div(class="desktop:text-xl")
                    | LISA's reporting and analytical capabilities allows us to be up to date in relation to over 30,000 claims and REO's we have acquired.  LISA's systems architecture creates a link between certified collection partners and legal offices working in the workout on the acquired portfolios and our team.
            .mb-10
                .text-2xl.font-serif.mb-3(class="desktop:text-4xl")
                    | Viewing and analyzing data
                div(class="desktop:text-xl")
                    | By harnessing the power of data   we ensure that our investments are backed by thorough analysis and insights driving growth and value in every acquisition we undertake.                                           
                                        
        h2.text-4xl.font-serif.mb-6(class="desktop:text-5xl desktop:mb-10")
            | Core reports
        div(class="desktop:grid desktop:grid-cols-2 desktop:mb-6")    
            .mb-10(class="desktop:text-xl desktop:pr-30")
                | test
            .mb-10
                img.size-full(src=require("../assets/monitor.png"))                                                                                                                                                 

